content: what day is it today Tuesday as an example and how many of those day are in the year 2026

Good afternoon! Today is Saturday, February 7th, 2026.

There are two Tuesdays in a week, so there are 52 Tuesdays in a year (52 weeks x 2 Tuesdays per week).

In the year 2026, there are:

* 365 days (not leap year)
* Approximately 183 Tuesdays
